# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Morpheus Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# The .env file is gitignored and will NOT be committed to version control.
# Share secrets securely with your team (see docs/guides/ENV_SETUP.md).
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED: Hetzner Cloud API Token
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your token from: https://console.hetzner.cloud/
# Navigate to: Security → API Tokens → Generate API Token
# Permissions needed: Read & Write
#
HETZNER_API_TOKEN=

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIONAL: Hetzner DNS API Token
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only needed if using Hetzner DNS for automatic DNS record management.
# Get your token from: https://dns.hetzner.com/settings/api-token
# If not set, HETZNER_API_TOKEN will be used as fallback.
#
# HETZNER_DNS_TOKEN=

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIONAL: Hetzner StorageBox Password
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only needed if using Hetzner StorageBox for shared registry storage.
# This allows multiple team members to share forest state.
#
# STORAGEBOX_PASSWORD=

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIONAL: Configuration Override
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Override the default config file location.
# Default search order: ./config.yaml, ~/.morpheus/config.yaml
#
# MORPHEUS_CONFIG_PATH=/path/to/your/config.yaml

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIONAL: Proxmox VE Configuration (for local/homelab VR nodes)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only needed if using Proxmox as your machine provider for VR node management.
# Create an API token in Proxmox: Datacenter → Permissions → API Tokens
#
# PROXMOX_HOST=192.168.1.100
# PROXMOX_API_TOKEN=your-api-token-secret
# PROXMOX_TOKEN_ID=morpheus@pam!morpheus-token
# PROXMOX_NODE=pve
#
# VM IDs for boot mode switching (pre-created VMs in Proxmox)
# PROXMOX_LINUX_VMID=101
# PROXMOX_WINDOWS_VMID=102
# PROXMOX_GPU_PCI=0000:01:00

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Team Sharing Guide
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# NEVER commit .env files with real secrets to version control!
#
# Secure methods to share .env files with your team:
#
# 1. Password Manager (Recommended)
#    - Store in 1Password, Bitwarden, or similar
#    - Create a shared vault for team secrets
#    - Team members download and save as .env
#
# 2. Encrypted File Sharing
#    - Use `age` or `gpg` to encrypt before sharing:
#      $ age -p .env > .env.age
#    - Share .env.age via Slack/email
#    - Decrypt: age -d .env.age > .env
#
# 3. Secret Management Service
#    - AWS Secrets Manager, HashiCorp Vault, Doppler, etc.
#    - Best for production/CI environments
#
# 4. Git-crypt or SOPS (for committed encrypted secrets)
#    - Encrypts specific files in the repo
#    - Team members with keys can decrypt locally
#
# See docs/guides/ENV_SETUP.md for detailed instructions.
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
